## About The Project

FounderLens is an AI-powered business intelligence platform that helps analyze businesses and generate strategic insights.

The platform evaluates a business through SWOT analysis, marketing audits, sales assessments, automation recommendations, and growth roadmaps, providing a structured overview of business performance and improvement opportunities.

This project was built as a portfolio project to demonstrate frontend development, dashboard design, business analysis concepts, and AI-driven product thinking.

